description:
Pitch Battle - Series 1, Episode 5




The six groups in this episode include young chamber choir Tring Park 16, musical theatre enthusiasts from the West Midlands Crescendo, Oxford University a cappella group Oxford Alternotives, classical quintet Vox-Xover, all-female pop group Vocalities and all-male barbershop chorus The Ramparts. They must impress the panel of musical judges - Gareth Malone, Kelis and guest judge Joe Jonas.




Original Air Date: 15-Jul-2017
